<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mappi · Marketingová strategie 2026</title>
<style>
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: normal;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: normal;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: italic;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 500;
  font-style: normal;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 500;
  font-style: italic;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: normal;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Sofia Pro Soft';
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: italic;
  src: url('data:font/otf;base64,') format('opentype');
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --blue: #2B3FE0;
  --blue-light: #4F61FF;
  --blue-dim: rgba(43,63,224,0.12);
  --blue-dim2: rgba(43,63,224,0.06);
  --dark: #0A0B14;
  --dark2: #111220;
  --dark3: #1A1C2E;
  --mid: #2A2D45;
  --muted: #6B7099;
  --soft: #A0A4C0;
  --white: #F4F5FF;
  --accent: #7FEFBD;
  --accent2: #FFD96A;
  --font: 'Sofia Pro Soft', sans-serif;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: var(--font);
  color: var(--white);
  background: var(--dark);
  overflow-x: hidden;
  cursor: none;
}

/* ── Cursor ── */
.cursor {
  position: fixed; width: 10px; height: 10px;
  background: var(--blue-light); border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999;
  transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  transition: transform 0.08s;
}
.cursor-ring {
  position: fixed; width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(79,97,255,0.35); border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 9998;
  transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
  transition: left 0.15s ease, top 0.15s ease;
}

/* ── Grid background ── */
.grid-bg {
  position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(43,63,224,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(43,63,224,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
}
.blob {
  position: fixed; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(120px); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}
.blob-1 { width: 700px; height: 700px; background: rgba(43,63,224,0.07); top: -250px; right: -200px; }
.blob-2 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: rgba(127,239,189,0.04); bottom: -150px; left: -150px; }

/* ── Progress sidebar ── */
.progress {
  position: fixed; left: 36px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; z-index: 200;
}
.dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 3px;
  background: var(--mid); cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s, height 0.3s;
}
.dot.active { background: var(--blue-light); height: 24px; }
.dot:hover { background: var(--soft); }

/* ── Slide counter ── */
.counter {
  position: fixed; bottom: 36px; left: 40px;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--muted); z-index: 200; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.counter span { color: var(--soft); }

/* ── SLIDES ── */
.slide {
  min-height: 100vh; width: 100%; position: relative;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 80px 80px 80px 120px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(43,63,224,0.1);
  z-index: 1;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
}

/* scroll snap on html */
html {
  scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
}

.slide > .content {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  width: 100%; max-width: 1080px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── Type ── */
.label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue-light);
  margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;
}
h1 {
  font-size: clamp(52px, 7.5vw, 96px); font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 0.96; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--white);
}
h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue-light); }
h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue-light); }
h2 {
  font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 58px); font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--white);
}
h3 {
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px;
}
p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--soft); font-weight: 400; }
.large { font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 22px); line-height: 1.6; }
.hl { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }
.accent-text { color: var(--accent); }
.blue-text { color: var(--blue-light); }
.yellow-text { color: var(--accent2); }
.divider { width: 44px; height: 3px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 2px; margin: 22px 0; }

/* ── Layout ── */
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; }
.full-col { width: 100%; }
.stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
.stack-tight { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }

/* ── Cards ── */
.card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--mid);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 26px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.card:hover { border-color: rgba(79,97,255,0.4); }
.card-accent { border-left: 3px solid var(--blue-light); }
.card-green { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); background: rgba(127,239,189,0.03); }
.card-yellow { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2); background: rgba(255,217,106,0.03); }

/* ── Quote block ── */
.quote-block {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
  padding: 20px 26px;
  background: var(--blue-dim);
  border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
}
.quote-block p { color: var(--white); font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; }

/* ── Tags ── */
.tag {
  display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  border: 1px solid; margin: 3px 3px 3px 0;
}
.tag-blue { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue-light); background: var(--blue-dim); }
.tag-green { border-color: rgba(127,239,189,0.3); color: var(--accent); background: rgba(127,239,189,0.06); }
.tag-yellow { border-color: rgba(255,217,106,0.3); color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(255,217,106,0.06); }

/* ── Audience table ── */
.aud-header {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mid); margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.aud-header div {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
}
.aud-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,69,0.7);
  align-items: start;
}
.aud-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.aud-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.4; }
.aud-name small { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 2px; }
.aud-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--soft); line-height: 1.55; padding-right: 20px; }
.aud-msg { font-size: 14px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1.55; font-style: italic; }

/* ── Channel rows ── */
.channel-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
.channel-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr auto;
  align-items: start; gap: 24px;
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--mid);
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 24px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.channel-row:hover { border-color: rgba(79,97,255,0.35); }
.ch-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); padding-top: 2px; }
.ch-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--soft); line-height: 1.5; }
.ch-phase {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
  white-space: nowrap; margin-top: 2px;
}
.phase-1 { background: rgba(43,63,224,0.18); color: var(--blue-light); border: 1px solid rgba(43,63,224,0.4); }
.phase-2 { background: rgba(127,239,189,0.07); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(127,239,189,0.25); }

/* ── Broker section ── */
.broker-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px; }
.acq-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,69,0.7); }
.acq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.acq-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.acq-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--soft); line-height: 1.5; }
.acq-text strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }

/* ── Recap slide ── */
.recap-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 32px; }
.recap-card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--mid);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px 22px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
}
.recap-card:hover { border-color: rgba(79,97,255,0.4); transform: translateY(-3px); }
.recap-num {
  font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-light), var(--accent));
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text; margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.recap-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.recap-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

/* ── Cover specifics ── */
#slide-0 { justify-content: flex-start; padding-left: 120px; }
#slide-0 .eyebrow {
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 28px;
}
#slide-0 h1 { max-width: 820px; }
#slide-0 .sub {
  margin-top: 36px; font-size: 19px; color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 500px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 400;
}
#slide-0 .corner {
  position: absolute; bottom: 60px; right: 80px;
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid);
}

/* ── Light slides (1–5) ── */
.slide-light {
  background: #FFFFFF;
}
.slide-light h2,
.slide-light h3,
.slide-light .hl,
.slide-light .aud-name,
.slide-light .ch-name,
.slide-light .ch-name span,
.slide-light .recap-title,
.slide-light strong { color: #0A0B14; }
.slide-light h2 em { color: #2B3FE0; font-style: normal; }

.slide-light p,
.slide-light .aud-desc,
.slide-light .ch-desc,
.slide-light .acq-text,
.slide-light .recap-desc { color: #4A4E6A; }

.slide-light .label { color: var(--blue); }
.slide-light .muted-label { color: #9096B8; }

.slide-light .card {
  background: #F5F6FF;
  border-color: #DDE0F5;
}
.slide-light .card:hover { border-color: rgba(43,63,224,0.35); }
.slide-light .card-green { background: #F2FEF8; border-left-color: #2ECC8A; }
.slide-light .card-yellow { background: #FFFBEF; border-left-color: #E8B800; }
.slide-light .card-accent { background: #F5F6FF; border-left-color: var(--blue-light); }

.slide-light .quote-block {
  background: rgba(43,63,224,0.06);
  border-left-color: var(--blue);
}
.slide-light .quote-block p { color: #0A0B14; }

.slide-light .aud-header div { color: #9096B8; }
.slide-light .aud-row { border-bottom-color: #E8EAF5; }
.slide-light .aud-header { border-bottom-color: #DDE0F5; }
.slide-light .aud-msg { color: #2B3FE0; }

.slide-light .channel-row {
  background: #F5F6FF;
  border-color: #DDE0F5;
}
.slide-light .channel-row:hover { border-color: rgba(43,63,224,0.35); }

.slide-light .acq-item { border-bottom-color: #E8EAF5; }

.slide-light .tag-blue { background: rgba(43,63,224,0.08); color: var(--blue); border-color: rgba(43,63,224,0.25); }
.slide-light .tag-green { background: rgba(46,204,138,0.08); color: #1A9E6A; border-color: rgba(46,204,138,0.3); }

.slide-light .divider { background: var(--blue); }

.slide-light .counter { color: #9096B8; }
.slide-light .dot { background: #DDE0F5; }
.slide-light .dot.active { background: var(--blue); }
.slide-light .dot:hover { background: #9096B8; }
.slide-light .grid-bg { display: none; }

/* accent2 yellow on light = darker shade */
.slide-light .yellow-text,
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--accent2)"],
.slide-light .card-yellow h3 { color: #B8860B !important; }
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--accent)"] { color: #1A9E6A !important; }
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--blue-light)"] { color: var(--blue) !important; }
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--soft)"] { color: #4A4E6A !important; }
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--muted)"] { color: #9096B8 !important; }
.slide-light [style*="color:var(--white)"] { color: #0A0B14 !important; }
.slide-light .blue-text { color: var(--blue) !important; }
.slide-light .accent-text { color: #1A9E6A !important; }

/* border-bottom on slides */
.slide-light { border-bottom-color: #E8EAF5; }


/* ═══════════════════ RESPONSIVE — MOBILE ═══════════════════ */
@media (max-width: 768px) {

  /* Base layout */
  .slide {
    padding: 60px 24px 60px 24px;
    min-height: 100svh;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 72px;
  }
  #slide-0 {
    padding-left: 24px;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  #slide-0 h1 { max-width: 100%; }

  /* Typography */
  h1 { font-size: clamp(38px, 11vw, 56px); line-height: 1.0; }
  h2 { font-size: clamp(26px, 7.5vw, 40px); }

  /* Navigation dots — move to bottom */
  #progress {
    flex-direction: row;
    bottom: 16px;
    left: 50%;
    top: auto;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
  .dot.active { width: 18px; border-radius: 3px; }

  /* Counter */
  #counter { bottom: 14px; left: 24px; top: auto; }

  /* Two-column → single column */
  .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 32px !important; }

  /* Audience table → stacked cards */
  .aud-header { display: none; }
  .aud-row {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 16px 0;
  }
  .aud-name { font-size: 15px; }
  .aud-name small { display: inline; margin-left: 8px; font-size: 12px; }
  .aud-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .aud-msg {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent2);
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  /* Channel rows → stacked */
  .channel-row {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 8px !important;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .ch-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
  .ch-phase { justify-self: start; }

  /* Recap grid → 1 column */
  .recap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 12px !important; margin-top: 20px; }
  .recap-card { padding: 18px 16px; }
  .recap-num { font-size: 22px; width: 36px; height: 36px; }

  /* Trust pillar 3-col → 1 col */
  .slide [style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }
  /* Web problem 3-col → 1 col */
  #slide-prob [style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }
  /* Academy 2-col → 1 col */
  #slide-academy [style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }

  /* Broker slide flex header */
  #slide-5 .two-col > div:first-child { order: 1; }
  #slide-5 .stack { order: 2; }

  /* Inline flex headers with space-between → stack */
  .content > div[style*="justify-content:space-between"] {
    flex-direction: column !important;
    align-items: flex-start !important;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .content > div[style*="justify-content:space-between"] > p,
  .content > div[style*="justify-content:space-between"] > div {
    max-width: 100% !important;
    text-align: left !important;
  }

  /* Trust pillar bottom bar */
  .slide [style*="border-left:3px solid #2B3FE0"] p { font-size: 13px; }

  /* Cards */
  .card { padding: 14px 16px; }
  .card p { font-size: 13px; }

  /* Sub on cover */
  #slide-0 .sub { font-size: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }

  /* Label */
  .label { font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  /* Acq items */
  .acq-item { gap: 10px; }
  .acq-text { font-size: 13px; }

  /* Channel desc font */
  .ch-desc { font-size: 13px; }

  /* Stack gap reduction */
  .stack { gap: 10px; }

  /* Trust cards inner text */
  .slide [style*="background:#2B3FE0"] p,
  .slide [style*="background:#0A0B14"] p { font-size: 13px; }
}

@media (max-width: 420px) {
  h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 10vw, 44px); }
  h2 { font-size: clamp(22px, 8vw, 32px); }
  .slide { padding: 60px 18px 60px 18px; padding-top: 64px; }
}


@media (max-width: 768px) {
  html { scroll-snap-type: y proximity; }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>
<div class="grid-bg"></div>
<div class="blob blob-1"></div>
<div class="blob blob-2"></div>

<div class="progress" id="progress"></div>
<div class="counter"><span id="cs">1</span> / 9</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ SLIDE 0 — COVER ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="slide" id="slide-0" data-index="0">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="eyebrow">Mappi.gt · Marketing Strategy · 2026</div>
    <h1>Building<br><em>the first trusted</em><br>real estate portal<br>in Guatemala.</h1>
    <div class="sub">Five strategic pillars. One mission:<br>help one million families live better.</div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ SLIDE 1 — TRUST PILLAR ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="slide slide-light" id="slide-1" data-index="1">
  <div class="content">
    <span class="label">01 · Central Pillar</span>
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end; margin-bottom:32px;">
      <h2>Trust is not one part<br>of the strategy.<br><em>It is the entire strategy.</em></h2>
      <p style="max-width:300px; font-size:14px; text-align:right; color:#4A4E6A;">Every campaign, every post, every broker report — all of it is proof of one of three promises.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:20px; margin-bottom:28px;">
      <div style="background:#2B3FE0; border-radius:16px; padding:28px 24px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:14px;">Axis 1</div>
        <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:12px;">Brokers</div>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;">"Mappi will bring you leads and quality inquiries. We have your back."</p>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);">Pulso Mappi · Reporting · Mappi Academy</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#0A0B14; border-radius:16px; padding:28px 24px; border:1px solid #2A2D45;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6B7099;margin-bottom:14px;">Axis 2</div>
